<a href="http://apps.fas.usda.gov/psdonline/circulars/Dairy.pdf" target="_self">http://apps.fas.usda.gov/psdonline/circulars/dairy.pdf</a></p><p><i>Thecattlesite.com</i>, ‘Exports to dominate expanding global dairy market’, 30 June 2014</p><p>
<a href="http://www.thecattlesite.com/news/46032/exports-to-dominate-expanding-global-dairy-market" target="_self">http://www.thecattlesite.com/news/46032/exports-to-dominate-expanding-gl...</a></p><p><i>Agrimoney.com</i>, ‘Dairy prices hit 21-month low as China buying ebbs’, 16 July 2014</p><p>
<a href="http://www.agrimoney.com/news/dairy-prices-hit-21-month-low-as-china-buying-ebbs--7270.html" target="_self">http://www.agrimoney.com/news/dairy-prices-hit-21-month-low-as-china-buy...</a></p><p><i>Times of Zambia</i>, ‘Dairy farmers cry for milk items zero rating’, 13 August 2014</p><p>
